data.text:
@NYCanegirl @wechoosewisdom @megynkelly All accused have the right to due process. Over seven dozen cases have been filed against universities by men accused of sexual misconduct - and the vast majority of them have won.
The Obama DOE's "Dear Colleague" letter unconstitutionally deprives students of their due process.
@NYCanegirl @megynkelly “Too far in favor”, is there even such a thing?  An assault victim deserves all the assistance they can get....
